</p></list-item><list-item><p>The US Centers for Disease Control and Prevention provides information about <ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="http://www.cdc.gov/tb/">tuberculosis</ext-link> and about <ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="http://www.cdc.gov/tb/topic/treatment/default.htm">treatment for tuberculosis</ext-link> (in English and Spanish)</p></list-item><list-item><p>The US National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases also has detailed information on all aspects of <ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="http://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/tuberculosis/pages/default.aspx">tuberculosis</ext-link>
